  "title": "Paid Media Specialist (E-Commerce, Fashion/Apparel)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Create and execute paid media strategies across various online advertising channels such as <strong>Facebook Ads, Instagram Ads, Pinterest Ads, and Tiktok Ads.</strong></li>\n  <li>Work closely with the marketing team to ensure paid media campaigns align with overall marketing and business objectives.</li>\n  <li>Develop and handle paid media campaigns from start to finish, including budget allocation, targeting, and ongoing optimization.</li>\n  <li>Monitor campaign performance, analyse data, and give insights to improve Purchases, ROI, CPA, ROAS.</li>\n  <li>Keep abreast with industry trends, changes in algorithms, and new advertising platforms.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Digital Marketing or equivalent</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years of experience in handling <strong>paid media campaigns (Facebook Ads, Pinterest Ads, Tiktok Ads, etc.)</strong> in an <strong>E-Commerce, Fashion/Apparel sector.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge in ad campaign setup, optimization, and budget management.</li>\n  <li>Proficient with Google Analytics and A/B testing and conversion rate optimization.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
